  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Letters to the Devolved Administrations on the EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, Steve Barclay, has written to the Scottish and Welsh Governments to set out the UK Government’s position on their consideration of the Withdrawal Agreement Bill.</p>

  </div>
</div>

